@startuml checkout-sequence
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam maxMessageSize 220

title Checkout Transaction — Sequence Diagram

actor       User         as U
participant "Browser\n(React + Zustand)" as B  #E8F5E9
participant "sessionStorage"             as SS #FFF9C4
database    "URL params"                 as URL #E3F2FD
participant "Next.js API\nRoutes"        as API #E8EAF6
participant "Supabase\n(PostgreSQL)"     as DB  #FCE4EC
participant "Niubiz\n(Payment Gateway)"  as NIU #FFF3E0

== Phase 1 — Reserve Stock ==

U -> B : Click "Finalizar Compra"
activate B

B -> API : POST /api/checkout/reserve\n{items: [{volumeId, title, qty}]}
activate API

API -> DB : SELECT price FROM manga_volumes\n(re-fetch authoritative prices)
DB --> API : prices[]

API -> DB : RPC reserve_stock(\n  totalAmount, itemCount,\n  items[], ttl=300s\n)
note right of DB
  **ATOMIC PL/pgSQL**
  1. INSERT orders (status='pending', expires_at)
  2. FOR each item:
     - SELECT stock FOR UPDATE
     - Decrement inventory.stock
     - INSERT order_items
  3. RETURN {order_id, expires_at, purchase_number}
end note
DB --> API : {order_id, expires_at, purchase_number}

API --> B : 200 {orderId, expiresAt, purchaseNumber}
deactivate API

B -> SS : SET checkout_stock = stockSnapshot
B -> URL : Navigate to /checkout?\norderId=...&expiresAt=...&purchaseNumber=...

note over DB
  **DB State:** order.status = 'pending'
  inventory.stock decremented
  order_items.reserved_from_stock tracked
  **TTL:** 5 min auto-expire
end note

== Phase 2 — Delivery + Payment Session ==

U -> B : Fill email, phone, address\nClick "Pagar"
activate B

B -> API : POST /api/checkout/delivery\n{orderId, email, phone, address}
activate API
API -> DB : UPDATE orders SET email, phone, address
DB --> API : ok
API --> B : 200 {ok}
deactivate API

B -> API : POST /api/checkout/session\n{orderId}
activate API
API -> DB : SELECT total_amount, status,\npurchase_number FROM orders
DB --> API : {amount, 'pending', purchaseNumber}

API -> NIU : GET /api.security/v1/security\n(Basic Auth)
NIU --> API : accessToken

API -> NIU : POST /api.ecommerce/v2/\ntoken/session/{merchantId}\n{amount, channel, antifraud}
NIU --> API : {sessionKey, expirationTime}

API --> B : 200 {sessionToken, merchantId,\namount, purchaseNumber}
deactivate API

B -> SS : SET checkout_ctx =\n{orderId, merchantId, purchaseNumber}

B -> B : VisanetCheckout.configure({\n  sessionToken, merchantId,\n  purchaseNumber, amount,\n  action: /api/checkout/callback\n})
B -> B : VisanetCheckout.open()

note over B
  **Browser State:**
  status = 'paying'
  checkout_ctx in sessionStorage
end note

== Phase 3 — Niubiz Lightbox ==

U -> NIU : Enter card details\nin Lightbox iframe
activate NIU

alt User completes payment
    NIU -> API : POST /api/checkout/callback\n(form: transactionToken)
    activate API
    API -> URL : 303 Redirect → /checkout?\nstatus=callback&transactionToken=...
    deactivate API
    
    NIU --> B : (page navigates away)
    deactivate NIU
    
else User cancels / timeout
    NIU -> URL : Redirect → /checkout?status=timeout
    deactivate NIU
end

== Phase 4 — Verify & Authorize ==

B -> B : Page reloads.\nDetect status=callback from URL
activate B
B -> SS : GET checkout_ctx\n→ {orderId, merchantId, purchaseNumber}
B -> SS : DELETE checkout_ctx

B -> API : POST /api/checkout/verify\n{transactionId, merchantId,\norderId, purchaseNumber}
activate API

API -> DB : SELECT total_amount,\npurchase_number FROM orders
DB --> API : {amount, purchaseNumber}

API -> NIU : GET /api.security/v1/security
NIU --> API : accessToken

API -> NIU : **POST** /api.authorization/v3/\nauthorization/ecommerce/{merchantId}\n{tokenId, purchaseNumber,\namount, currency}
activate NIU
NIU --> API : {actionCode, TRANSACTION_ID,\nSTATUS, authorizedAmount}
deactivate NIU

alt actionCode == "000" (Approved)
    API -> DB : RPC confirm_order(\n  orderId, transactionId\n)
    note right of DB
      UPDATE orders
      SET status='completed',
          niubiz_transaction_id,
          expires_at=NULL
    end note
    DB --> API : {confirmed: true}
    API --> B : 200 {success: true,\ntransactionId, amount}
    
    B -> B : clearCart()\nsetStatus('success')
    B --> U : Show success screen\n"¡Compra realizada!\nMonto: S/ {amount}"

else actionCode != "000" (Denied)
    API -> DB : RPC release_reservation(orderId)
    note right of DB
      Restore inventory.stock
      SET order.status='expired'
    end note
    DB --> API : {released: true}
    API --> B : 200 {success: false,\nerrorMessage}
    
    B --> U : Show error\n"Transacción no aprobada"
end

deactivate API
deactivate B

== Compensating Actions (Background) ==

note over DB
  **pg_cron (every 60s):**
  cleanup_expired_reservations()
  → finds orders WHERE status='pending'
    AND expires_at < now()
  → calls release_reservation() for each
  → restores inventory.stock
  → marks order.status='expired'
end note

note over B
  **beforeunload listener:**
  If status='reserved' → sendBeacon
  POST /api/checkout/release {orderId}
  (best-effort, not guaranteed)
end note

@enduml
